descriptionNullable:
### **Context**
For Indonesian fragrance enthusiasts, it may take effort to discover Indonesian legit local perfume brand. In the dataset, you'll find plenty of brands represented by only one variant of their products to give you an idea of the brand in general. 

**Recently Added**
Akiko
Aksen
Art Derora
Avalanche
Beure
De Antoine
Dewdrop Perfumery

### **Content**

Brand = Brand or company of the perfume
Followers = Brand followers on Instagram (per November 2022 - February 2023)
Year = When the brand established
Variant = Name of the perfume (based on top sales section in Shopee except Fakhroul Oud, Hausser, Normal Estate, Azwary Perfume, Peculiar, and Leuseni)
Concentration = Concentration of perfume oils
Size = The size of perfume in milliliter (only fullbottle size included)
Price = Price in e-commerce
Price per ml = Price divided by size
Notes = Fragrance notes in perfume (a few brands written the description with main accords, not the notes)

### **Disclaimer**
If there is a mistake about the brand profile, the products, spelling, or there is new brand upcoming, feel free to edit it or contact me.
